---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const title = "AI Agent Setup | On PAR Dev";
const description = "Get a personal AI assistant system running on your own hardware. Always on, private, and fully yours.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">

      <section class="hero-section">
        <span class="badge">New Service</span>
        <h1>Your Own AI Agent System</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          A personal AI assistant that runs 24/7 on your hardware. It reads your calendar, checks your email, manages reminders, and connects to the messaging apps you already use. Private, local, and fully under your control.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="what-you-get">
        <h2>What You Get</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">üíª</span>
            <h3>Runs on Your Hardware</h3>
            <p>Mac Mini, MacBook, or any Mac with Apple Silicon. Your data stays on your machine.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">üí¨</span>
            <h3>Chat From Anywhere</h3>
            <p>Talk to your assistant through Telegram, Discord, or Signal. No special app needed.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">üìÖ</span>
            <h3>Calendar + Email Awareness</h3>
            <p>It knows your schedule, can check your inbox, and gives you a morning briefing every day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">üîí</span>
            <h3>Private by Default</h3>
            <p>No cloud dependency for your personal data. Local AI models available for zero-cost operation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</span>
            <h3>Customized to You</h3>
            <p>Configured for your workflow, your tools, your preferences. Not a one-size-fits-all chatbot.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">üìö</span>
            <h3>Walkthrough + Documentation</h3>
            <p>You'll understand how it works. I walk you through the system and leave you with clear docs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <span class="step-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Discovery Call</h3>
              <p>We talk about what you want your assistant to do. Calendar management? Email triage? Research? Content? We figure out the right setup for you.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="step-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Setup + Configuration</h3>
              <p>I install and configure OpenClaw on your machine, connect your messaging platform, wire up your calendar and email, and set up any custom agents you need.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="step-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Walkthrough + Handoff</h3>
              <p>Live walkthrough of your system. You'll know how to talk to it, how to customize it, and what to do if something goes wrong. Plus written docs for reference.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="pricing">
        <h2>Pricing</h2>
        <div class="pricing-cards">
          <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>Basic Setup</h3>
            <div class="price">$250</div>
            <p class="price-note">One-time</p>
            <ul>
              <li>OpenClaw installed and configured</li>
              <li>One messaging channel (Telegram or Discord)</li>
              <li>Calendar integration</li>
              <li>Morning briefing configured</li>
              <li>1 hour walkthrough + handoff</li>
              <li>Written documentation</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Started</a>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card featured">
            <span class="featured-badge">Most Popular</span>
            <h3>Full Setup</h3>
            <div class="price">$500</div>
            <p class="price-note">One-time</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Everything in Basic</li>
              <li>Multiple messaging channels</li>
              <li>Email integration</li>
              <li>Custom agent personas</li>
              <li>Scheduled reports and reminders</li>
              <li>Local AI model configuration</li>
              <li>2 hours walkthrough + handoff</li>
              <li>30 days email support</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Started</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="disclaimer">
        <h2>Important Notes</h2>
        <div class="disclaimer-content">
          <p><strong>OpenClaw is open-source beta software.</strong> I'll set it up and configure it for you, but I didn't build OpenClaw itself. Here's what you should know:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>OpenClaw is under active development. Updates may occasionally require reconfiguration.</li>
            <li>This service covers initial setup and configuration. Ongoing maintenance is your responsibility (though I'm happy to help on an hourly basis if needed).</li>
            <li>AI models (cloud or local) may incur their own costs depending on your usage and provider choices.</li>
            <li>You're responsible for your own API keys, accounts, and any data you give the system access to.</li>
            <li>No guarantees of uptime, accuracy, or fitness for any particular purpose. This is a power-user tool, not a consumer product (yet).</li>
            <li>By purchasing this service, you acknowledge that you use OpenClaw at your own risk.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
        <p>Interested? Have questions? Reach out and we'll figure out if this is a good fit.</p>
        <div class="contact-methods">
          <a href="mailto:patrick@onpardev.com" class="contact-link">üìß patrick@onpardev.com</a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/patrick-robinson-dev" target="_blank" class="contact-link">üíº LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    padding-top: 80px;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-12);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--base-100);
    color: var(--text-700);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border: 1px solid var(--base-200);
  }

  .hero-section h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
    color: var(--text-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .feature {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border: 1px solid var(--base-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: white;
    transition: transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease;
  }

  .feature:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .steps li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--text-900);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .steps h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .steps p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pricing-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-8);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--base-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-10);
    background: white;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pricing-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--text-900);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--text-900);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .pricing-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    color: var(--text-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .price-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-500);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .pricing-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .pricing-card li {
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-700);
  }

  .pricing-card li::before {
    content: '‚úì';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--text-900);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--text-900);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 200ms ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .disclaimer {
    background: var(--base-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--base-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-10);
  }

  .disclaimer h2 {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .disclaimer-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .disclaimer-content ul {
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .disclaimer-content li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .contact-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  }

  .contact-section p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--text-600);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--text-900);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: opacity 200ms ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .pricing-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .contact-methods {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
